Package: vecnet
Type: Package
Title: Vectorization of Road Networks From Rasters and Airborne Laser Scanning
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Jean-Romain Roussel
Maintainer: Jean-Romain Roussel <jean-romain.roussel.1@ulaval.ca>
Description: Functions to vectorize raster of roads. It works with binary and non binary raster, is robust to false positive, false negative and returns a topologically valid set of spatial lines.
License: GPL-3
